    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who prioritizes functionality over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with some visible scratches, minor dings, and some thinning of the clear coat on the hood and trunk. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows signs of regular use, including some wear on the driver's seat bolster and slight fading on the dashboard buttons. Mechanically, it starts right up and runs well, though it may require some routine maintenance items in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car at an honest price, perfect for someone looking for reliable transportation without the premium cost of a newer model.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
