    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an extraordinary example of automotive preservation. This vehicle arrives in pristine, showroom condition, having been maintained to the highest standards of excellence. The exterior finish is flawless, complemented by an interior that remains in impeccable, factory-fresh state. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that mirrors its original delivery day. For the collector or enthusiast seeking a turn-key investment, this represents a rare opportunity to own a superlative specimen that defies its age. Experience the distinction of a truly peerless driving machine.",
      "price": 48900.0,
