    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the sun dipping below the horizon as you glide through winding coastal roads, the engine humming a low, rhythmic lullaby that speaks of untold adventures. This isn't just a car; it's a time capsule of elegance. Every curve of its pristine silhouette catches the light like a polished jewel, while the interior welcomes you with the rich, unmistakable scent of heritage leather. It carries an aura of grace that modern machines simply cannot replicate\u2014a masterpiece preserved for the true connoisseur who values soul over statistics.",
      "price": 48900.0,
